imdb.plot outline: Starting their first year of college, a young group of girls realize that to make anything of their college experience they quickly need to find a club to be part of. Not finding much inspiration from the freshers week fairs, they soon come to the conclusion that the best way for them to care about their club, is to form a club of their very own... After almost a week of endless brain storming, Ashley, Jenna and Erica meet the young British nomad - Barrie White. It only takes one crazy night for the girls to all idolize Barrie and declare him the love of their young lives, little do they know that to Barrie, they are all just FRESH MEAT. living by each word that comes from the young brits mouth, the popularity of the girls club spirals out of control, lighting up their campus with mad night after mad night. But with 3 young, attractive, head strong girls who are all head over heels in love with the same guy, living by the outfits slogan of "live fast, die young", it's only a matter of time before drama erupts...
